<bug>
	<id>4780</id>
	<title>[Feature] Git URI support for ADD</title>
	<description>
		<paragraph id="1">
			<sentence id="1.1">In order to better support building out projects inside a docker container, docker should support git URIs.</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="2">
			<sentence id="2.1">```
 ADD git@github.com:Fuzion24/MyRepo.git#TAG /opt/MyRepo/
```
TAG here could be a git tag, branch, or commit hash.</sentence>
		</paragraph>
	</description>
</bug>
